<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Stray Cat Feeding Stations - Public Viewers</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            position: relative;
        }
        .container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            position: relative;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .content {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }
        .join-section {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .join-section button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-right: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .join-section button:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }
        .join-section a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #4CAF50;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .error-message {
            color: red;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        th, td {
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
            text-align: center;
        }
        th {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        td {
            background-color: #fff;
        }
        img {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            right: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            margin-right: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Welcome to the Stray Cat Feeding Stations</h1>
            <p>This website is dedicated to helping stray cats in Qatar by providing information about feeding stations where they gather in larger numbers.</p>
            <p>Our mission is to promote volunteerism to ensure that these cats receive food and, if needed, medical attention.</p>
            <p>If you're interested in helping, please consider volunteering or donating to support our cause.</p>
            <p>Thank you for your compassion towards stray animals!</p>
            <p>- The Local Animal Shelter</p>
            <!-- Error message section -->
            {{#if errorMessage}}
            <div class="error-message">
                {{errorMessage}}
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            <!-- Join section with login and sign up buttons -->
            <div class="join-section">
                <a href="/register">Sign Up</a> | <a href="/login">Log In</a>
            </div>
            <!-- Table section -->
            <div>
                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Feeding Station</th>
                        <th>Location</th>
                    </tr>
                    {{#each locations}}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{this.name}}</td>
                        <td><a href="{{this.location}}">{{this.location}}</a></td>
                    </tr>
                    {{/each}}
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
